io.micronaut.aot.core.codegen

Class ApplicationContextConfigurerGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.micronaut.aot.core.codegen.AbstractCodeGenerator
      • io.micronaut.aot.core.codegen.ApplicationContextConfigurerGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AOTCodeGenerator

    public class ApplicationContextConfigurerGenerator
extends AbstractCodeGenerator
    The "optimized" entry point generator is the main source generator: it is responsible for generating a new entry point, which delegates to the original entry point of the application, and injects a number of optimizations before starting the application. The list of optimizations to inject is determined by the list of delegate optimizers which are passed to this generator.
